ai-kv8.1:1.4_0: “The animal realm is the ghost realm, humanity, and the gods.”
ai-kv8.1:1.6_0: The Buddha has spoken of five kinds of one:
ai-kv8.1:1.7_0: hell, the animal realm, the ghost realm, humanity, and the gods.
ai-kv8.1:2.3_0: Do not die any (consequence) in the morning time when the Dragons had gathered together with the adornments of the gods.
ai-kv8.1:2.5_0: And when he’s killed, he never returns to their homes.
ai-kv8.1:3.3_0: The gods of Vepacitti, having gathered round, surrounded by the gods of the Thirty-Three, together with the gods of the Thirty-Three, went to a gathering.
ai-kv8.1:3.5_0: that Vepacitti was killed when the gods had gathered. He then gathered together with the gods of the Thirty-Three, not looking down on the same day.
ai-kv8.1:4.3_0: Have the ears that are prevented by Vepacitti,
ai-kv8.1:5.6_0: And there is a razor-worker who will not be told,
ai-kv8.1:5.8_0: The account of the group of six is finished.
